[30;1m2 | [0m[35mThe swiftclient.SwiftService API[0m
[30;1m3 | [0m[35m================================[0m
[30;1m4 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m5 | [0m[35mA higher-level API aimed at allowing developers an easy way to perform multiple[0m
[30;1m6 | [0m[35moperations asynchronously using a configurable thread pool. Documentation for[0m
[30;1m7 | [0m[35meach service method call can be found here: :mod:`swiftclient.service`.[0m
